“Home is a feeling. What better feeling to have than being accepted & valued by the people closest to us?”

Like this post & we’ll donate. We’re obsessed with this young activist’s bedroom makeover and Q&A. 😍 @genesisbutler_ is an advocate for animal rights, and one of the youngest people to ever give a TEDx talk (#nbd). An ethical vegan since she was 6—she started @genesisforanimals, which provides funding to sanctuaries and rescues that provide animals with a permanent home. For each like this post gets, we will donate $3 toward Genesis’ causes (full donation amount up to $1500). Funding will go towards the care of animals including food, shelter, transportation costs, surgeries, and vet visits. Charity contact information: genesisforanimals@yahoo.org. Runs from 4/23 - 4/30.

Wall storage is an often overlooked method of decluttering, but we think kids’ fave toys can be the best decor. Our Beaumont Wall Rack has four fixed shelves (for their sunglasses collection) plus pegs for hanging. 😎 The matching Beaumont Paper Roll Holder and Bins create an instant arts & craft station. 🎨 Tap to shop & bring your playroom to life. 🤍
#KidsArt #KidsDecor #Wainscoting #TealRoom #KidsStorage #GalleryWall #WallDecor #PlayroomDesign #PlayroomIdeas

@iammarleydias, the founder of #1000BlackGirlBooks, gets a total bedroom makeover (and surprises her mom with it).

→ “I loved the Roselle Desk because it combined the same curved edges I loved for my nightstand, dresser, chair and headboard. One thing I knew I really wanted was a full length mirror. I am so glad to have it and I’m excited to see my outfits in a new light.”

Tap through to see more of the space, including her reading/crochet corner. Shop her whole look at the link in bio.

Clutter control. 🚨 Looking to declutter your kid’s play space? Here’s a few ways to declutter this weekend:
1) Add a bookshelf for vertical storage for decor, toys and books. This gorgeous black Jenny Lind bookcase features intricate wood turnings and five sturdy open shelves. (Don’t forget the storage bins on the bottom shelf for easy-to-reach access.) 
2) Wall shelves are ideal for small spaces where floor real estate is limited. Simple, stylish and multifunctional, our wood shelf with hooks is Scandi-inspired and family-friendly. Your little one can hang their hat (ha!) and other clothing or toys from the hooks. 
3) Our best-selling Walnut and White Mid-Century Bookcase offers reachable storage with stylish design.
